OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FThe recent introduction of a
OL,7,Fregularisation scheme and increased
OL,8,Fmobility for employment permit holders
OL,9,Fhas helped prevent the irregular
OL,10,Femployment of migrant workers, a
OL,11,Freport has found.
OL,13,FResearch published on Tuesday by
OL,14,FEuropean Migration Network Ireland and
OL,15,FEsri (Economic and Social Research
OL,16,FInstitute), shows that the irregular
OL,17,Femployment of non-EU nationals occurs
OL,18,Facross a range of sectors in Ireland,
OL,19,Fparticularly in food service and
OL,20,Fwithin small enterprises.
