OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FThe food service activity sector
OL,7,Faccounted for 54% of employment permit
OL,8,Flaw breaches in 2023 with 12% in hair
OL,9,Fand beauty, and 11% in wholesale, the
OL,10,Freport found.
OL,12,FIrregular employment presents problems
OL,13,Ffor the state in terms of tax revenue
OL,14,Fand regulation, whether it is
OL,15,Fundertaken by Irish or non-Irish
OL,16,Fnationals.
