OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FThe report includes situations in
OL,7,Fwhich non-EU nationals are employed in
OL,8,Fundeclared work, work outside the
OL,9,Fconditions of their residence permits,
OL,10,For work while irregularly residing in
OL,11,Fthe country.
OL,13,FThe report stated that for non-EU
OL,14,Fnationals, working in an irregular
OL,15,Fsituation can create precarity,
OL,16,Fincluding difficulties accessing
OL,17,Fsocial security.
