OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FUndocumented workers may also be
OL,7,Freluctant to report poor working
OL,8,Fconditions because of a fear of losing
OL,9,Ftheir job or being deported, it went
OL,10,Fon to say.
OL,12,FEmployment inspections are led by the
OL,13,FWorkplace Relations Commission (WRC),
OL,14,Fto check compliance with employment
OL,15,Flaw.
OL,17,FIn 2023, 4,727 employment inspection
OL,18,Fcases were undertaken and 293 breaches
OL,19,Fof employment permits legislation were
OL,20,Fdetected.
