OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FHowever, the report has raised
OL,7,Fconcerns over the number of employment
OL,8,Finspectors, questioning the
OL,9,Feffectiveness of enforcement efforts.
OL,10,FIn January 2024, 63 WRC inspectors
OL,11,Fwere operating nationally.
OL,13,FRevenue data indicates that there were
OL,14,F191,600 employers in the state in
OL,15,F2023, which gives an overall
OL,16,Finspection rate of 2.5%.
OL,18,FThe number of WRC inspectors is
OL,19,Fplanned to increase to 80 during 2024.
