OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,F"This is particularly important in
OL,7,Flight of the steep increase in
OL,8,Femployment permits issued in recent
OL,9,Fyears, and the planned introduction of
OL,10,Fa new seasonal employment permit," the
OL,11,Freport said.
OL,13,F"While addressing irregular employment
OL,14,Fis not found to be a policy priority
OL,15,Fin itself, the regularisation of
OL,16,Fundocumented migrants emerged as a
OL,17,Fpivotal related strategy in Ireland in
OL,18,Frecent years."
