OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FUnder the scheme targeting
OL,7,Fundocumented former students, 2,253
OL,8,Fpeople have been granted residence,
OL,9,Fand since the introduction of the 2022
OL,10,FRegularisation of Long-Term
OL,11,FUndocumented Migrants Scheme, 4,617
OL,12,Fpeople granted residence.
OL,14,FUnder the migrants scheme, 55% of
OL,15,Fthose were in employment and 11% were
OL,16,Fself-employed.
OL,18,FData also shows that half were
OL,19,Femployed in one of three sectors
OL,20,Fincluding hospitality/tourism, food
OL,21,Fand drink, and cleaning/maintenance.
