OL,3,CIrregular employment of migrant
OL,4,Cworkers falls following new laws
OL,6,FThe Employment Permits Act 2024 also
OL,7,Fincludes new measures allowing workers
OL,8,Fon general or critical skills
OL,9,Femployment permits to change employers
OL,10,Fwithout needing to apply for a new
OL,11,Fpermit.
OL,13,FPreviously, holders of general
OL,14,Femployment permits could change
OL,15,Femployers only after one year and
OL,16,Fneeded a new permit to do so. New 2024
OL,17,Fregulations set the minimum period
OL,18,Fbefore changing at nine months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
